videos.headline: Florida INT hauls Vanderbilt drive
videos.description: Teez Tabor picks off Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur for his eighth interception of the year.

videos.headline: Gators rock Vandy QB on sack
videos.description: Florida DB Quincy Wilson blasts Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur for the sack.

videos.headline: Florida RB fights way for only TD of game
videos.description: Florida RB Jordan Scarlett runs it in from 4-yards out for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: J. Scarlett 24-yard run to put Gators in red zone
videos.description: Jordan Scarlett run for 24 yds to the Vandy 18 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Vanderbilt punter can't handle snap
videos.description: Vanderbilt punter Sam Loy can't handle the snap Florida recovers deep in Commodores territory.

videos.headline: Gators fumble away golden opportunity
videos.description: On 2nd and goal from the 1-yard line, Florida fumbles with a chance to put Vanderbilt away and the Commodores recover.

videos.headline: Florida interception seals win over Vanderbilt
videos.description: Wade Freebeck pass intercepted Nick Washington return for no gain to the Vandy 49

videos.headline: Gators need to get back to work after win over Vandy
videos.description: Florida head coach Jim McElwain discusses the Gators' performance against the Commodores.
